      <title>Markdown中部署Jupyter Notebook</title>
      <link href="2021/04/22/Deploy-Jupyter-In-Markdown/"/>
      <url>2021/04/22/Deploy-Jupyter-In-Markdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装与使用Jupyter-Notebook"><a href="#安装与使用Jupyter-Notebook" class="headerlink" title="安装与使用Jupyter Notebook"></a>安装与使用Jupyter Notebook</h1><ul><li>在镜像站下载  <code>pip install -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple jupyter</code></li><li>在工作目录文件夹下打开cmd，并输入jupyter即可</li></ul><h1 id="部署Jupyter-Notebook"><a href="#部署Jupyter-Notebook" class="headerlink" title="部署Jupyter Notebook"></a>部署Jupyter Notebook</h1><ul><li>感谢 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/The_last_knight/article/details/109391184">The_last_knight</a> </li></ul><ol><li><p>将 .ipynb 文件上传到 Github 中，然后复制文件在 Github 中的链接，例如<br><code>https://github.com/gtxygyzb/gtxygyzb.github.io/blob/main/study%20notes/Pandas%20study%20notes.ipynb</code></p></li><li><p>打开 <a href="https://nbviewer.jupyter.org/">https://nbviewer.jupyter.org/</a> 复制 1. 中的链接进入Jupyter浏览页面（如下图），若404换个时间再尝试</p></li></ol><p><img src="/2021/04/22/Deploy-Jupyter-In-Markdown/0.png"></p><ol start="3"><li><p>复制该页面的链接，然后在Markdown文件中使用ifname引用该链接，如</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>iframe</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>https://nbviewer.jupyter.org/github/gtxygyzb/gtxygyzb.github.io/blob/main/study%20notes/Pandas%20study%20notes.ipynb<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">width</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>100%<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">height</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>600<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>iframe</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre></li><li><p>效果如下图所示，每次本地.ipynb更新完重复步骤1和2即可，<strong>注意在github中，文件的路径和名称等要保持一致</strong></p></li></ol><p><img src="/2021/04/22/Deploy-Jupyter-In-Markdown/1.png"></p><ul><li>由于网络等因素，导致每次修改再部署耗费时间长，直接Jupyter转Markdown在阅读起来能接受的情况下是最方便的选择</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
